 `1 <= product.length <= products.length`\n\n- `amount.length == product.length`\n\n- `product[j]` exists in `products`.\n\n- `1 <= amount[j] <= 1000`\n\n- The elements of `product` are **unique**.\n\n- At most `1000` calls will be made to `getBill`.\n\n- Answers within `10⁻⁵` of the actual value will be accepted.","problemLink":"https://leetcode.com/problems/apply-discount-every-n-orders/","problemName":"Apply Discount Every n Orders","problemNumber":1357,"problemSlug":"apply-discount-every-n-orders","schemaVersion":2,"sequenceIndex":1357,"solutionApproaches":[]},{"assets":[],"categories":["Hash Table","String","Sliding Window"],"constraintBlocks":[],"contentBlocks":[{"sequence":0,"text":"Given a string `s` consisting only of characters *a*, *b* and *c*.\n\nReturn the number of substrings containing **at least** one occurrence of all these characters *a*, *b* and *c*.\n\n**Example 1:**","type":"text"},{"sequence":1,"text":"Input: s = \"abcabc\"\nOutput: 10\nExplanation: The substrings containing at least one occurrence of the characters a, b and c are \"abc\", \"abca\", \"abcab\", \"abcabc\", \"bca\", \"bcab\", \"bcabc\", \"cab\", \"cabc\" and \"abc\" (again). ","type":"code"},{"sequence":2,"text":"**Example 2:**","type":"text"},{"sequence":3,"text":"Input: s = \"aaacb\"\nOutput: 3\nExplanation: The substrings containing at least one occurrence of the characters a, b and c are \"aaacb\", \"aacb\" and \"acb\". ","type":"code"},{"sequence":4,"text":"**Example 3:**","type":"text"},{"sequence":5,"text":"Input: s = \"abc\"\nOutput: 1","type":"code"},{"sequence":6,"text":"**Constraints:**\n\n- `3 <= s.length <= 5 x 10⁴`\n\n- `s` only consists of `'a'`, `'b'` or `'c'` characters.","type":"text"}],"contentHtml":"","contentHtmlLocal":"","databaseEntry":{"categories":["Hash Table","String","Sliding Window"],"createdAt":0,"difficulty":"Medium","lastRevisionAt":0,"problem":"Given a string `s` consisting only of characters *a*, *b* and *c*.\n\nReturn the number of substrings co