s.length`.\n\n- `votes[i][j]` is an English **uppercase** letter.\n\n- All characters of `votes[i]` are unique.\n\n- All the characters that occur in `votes[0]` **also occur** in `votes[j]` where `1 <= j < votes.length`.","problemLink":"https://leetcode.com/problems/rank-teams-by-votes/","problemName":"Rank Teams by Votes","problemNumber":1366,"problemSlug":"rank-teams-by-votes","schemaVersion":2,"sequenceIndex":1366,"solutionApproaches":[]},{"assets":[{"assetIndex":0,"bytes":15158,"contentType":"image/png","localPath":"leetcode_seed/assets/problems/1367-linked-list-in-binary-tree/1367-sample_1_1720.png","originalUrl":"../../../images/1367-sample_1_1720.png","sha256":"ba41f1e13100745788d859b83b1c43a3834f2ccfce9878f7fc1c7ccea65ef21e"},{"assetIndex":1,"bytes":15451,"contentType":"image/png","localPath":"leetcode_seed/assets/problems/1367-linked-list-in-binary-tree/1367-sample_2_1720.png","originalUrl":"../../../images/1367-sample_2_1720.png","sha256":"f7f492e74c314ec1e165b59028ffda9fe5ab99b4295f9321e759f72ec5c32adc"}],"categories":["Linked List","Tree","Depth-First Search","Binary Tree"],"constraintBlocks":[],"contentBlocks":[{"sequence":0,"text":"Given a binary tree `root` and a linked list with `head` as the first node.\n\nReturn True if all the elements in the linked list starting from the `head` correspond to some *downward path* connected in the binary tree otherwise return False.\n\nIn this context downward path means a path that starts at some node and goes downwards.\n\n**Example 1:**\n\n**","type":"text"},{"alt":"Problem image","contentType":"image/png","localPath":"leetcode_seed/assets/problems/1367-linked-list-in-binary-tree/1367-sample_1_1720.png","sequence":1,"sha256":"ba41f1e13100745788d859b83b1c43a3834f2ccfce9878f7fc1c7ccea65ef21e","type":"image"},{"sequence":2,"text":"**","type":"text"},{"sequence":3,"text":"Input: head = [4,2,8], root = [1,4,4,null,2,2,null,1,null,6,8,null,null,null,null,1,3]\nOutput: true\nExplanation: Nodes in blue form a subpath in